Main periods of western civ

ancient period: 3500 bc - 500 ad

medieval period: 500 ad - 1500 ad

modern period: 1500 ad - presently

    early modern: 1500 ad - 1800 ad
        protestant reformation - french revolution
        Saw politically more divided states. More smaller states.

    recent modern: 1800 ad - present
        The rise of the concept of country.